text:
I'm looking for help to make my home page banner friendly for all devices.

I went in and added this query below by going to.. _Settings_ (top center tab in page editor) &gt; scroll to _Advanced Options_ and toggle down &gt; add in the _code snippets Head HTML,_ but it's still not updating my devices. Any advice on how to get this to display properly?
```&lt;style&gt;
@media (max-width: 600px) {
.hs_cos_gallery_slide .slick-slide .slick-current .slick-active {
max-width: 100% !important;
height: auto !important;
}
}
&lt;/style&gt;```
